# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# PERSONAL / LOCAL FILES  (yours, NOT part of the project)
# Everything in _personal/ is gitignored: your secrets, local
# LiteLLM proxy config and private notes live there. The project
# stays reproducible via the committed templates
# config.example.yaml and .env.example instead.
#
# .claude/ holds local Claude Code settings (e.g. the proxy that
# points at your localhost LiteLLM) — also excluded.
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.claude/
_personal/
